This will be a comprehensive compilment of Mod's, Macro's and everything else related to the Sovol Sv08.

You can contribute by making a pull-request, creating an issue, or starting a discussion.

None of the links found here are affiliate links.

I am using this as an outline to place a catalog of mods that I find.



Just Received Your Printer? You should probably:

  Update your firmware before you do anything else. There is a new firmware available since the printer first started shipping which is reported to possibly fix some print issues and error codes.
     Purchase a https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CQLVNZZC?psc=1&ref=ppx_yo2ov_dt_b_product_details
    This will ensure that you can revive your emmc should you brick it.



Outline

  1.Printed Upgrades
    
    a. Alternative More Printable SV08 Toolhead Cover by ectoBRUH
      1.Print your own more easily with this model. https://www.printables.com/model/850271-sovol-sv08-alternative-toolhead-cover
    b. SOVOL SV08 M12 Inductive Probe Mount LJ12A3-4-Z/AX
      1. https://www.printables.com/model/870302-sovol-sv08-m12-inductive-probe-mount-lj12a3-4-zax
    c. Klicky Probe Mod by Nadir
      1. Klicky probe is picked up by the printhead to be used for leveling then put back in a holder before printing. Klicky probes 
         are typical on Voron 2.4 printers and ensure that you will get repeatable measurements on both a cold start heatsoaked after hours printing.
      2. https://www.printables.com/model/849409-klicky-probe-for-sovol-sv08-abl
          a. Other Info
            1. https://www.reddit.com/r/Sovol/comments/1c82929/klicky_probe_mod_for_sovol_sv08/
  2. Modifications
     a. Cheaper HDMI Touchscreen
        1. https://a.co/d/9QO7IUP
     b. Din Rail for added electronics
        2. https://www.printables.com/model/867676-sovol-sv08-recessed-din-rail-mount-bracket
     c. Changing Stock inductive probe for more consistent z-offset

    

